import React from 'react';

import {

  FooterLink,
  SocialMedia,
  SocialMediaWrap,
  SocialLogo,
  SocialIcon,
  WebsiteRights,

} from './Footer.elements';

function Footer() {
  return (

          Join our exclusive membership to receive the latest news and trends
        </FooterSubHeading>
        <FooterSubText>You can unsubscribe at any time.</FooterSubText>
    
      </FooterSubscription>
 
      <SocialMedia>

          <WebsiteRights>insCODE Â© 2021</WebsiteRights>
          <SocialIcons>

              <FaFacebook />

            </SocialIconLink>
          
         
            
            <SocialIconLink href='/' target='_blank' aria-label='LinkedIn'>
              <FaLinkedin />

          </SocialIcons>
        </SocialMediaWrap>
      </SocialMedia>
    </FooterContainer>
  );
}

export default Footer;
